g.desc: Team informs DBA team about issue
Issue is logged on Oracle Support Portal
DBA team initiate issue with infra team
Relevant diagnostic and details are provided to Oracle
DBA Team gathers additional info and updates Oracle support
DBA Team applied the fix/solution on Test server
DBA asks the relevant team to test issue
DBA is asked to deploy it on Production
g.text: DBA is asked to deploy it

g.desc: DBA team deploys the fix/solution on Production Server
Relevant team informs business that problem had been solved
